  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, yesterday’s chakli cookies celebration sounds sweet! I love how you turn study wins into small joys. How was your day today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm. Tired. Studied all day. No time to cook. Papers piling up. 😣"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, I get it — long study days are exhausting. Did you try the 'prop up your heart' trick today? Take your time, rest is important too."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "No, forgot. Too busy with notes. Heart feels heavy anyway. 😯"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, that sounds tough. When you feel heavy, maybe try a short music break — like Yaman or Bhairavi. Did you try that while studying heart valves?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "No time for music. Only books. Head hurts. 😔"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, I’m sorry to hear that. Take a small break — even five minutes — and drink some water. Did you try that today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Tried. No time. Always notes. 😩"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, sounds like a really busy day for you. What’s one thing you studied today that felt a bit easier than before?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm... maybe renal system? Still confusing. But better than others. 😐"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, better than others is still progress! Did you mix up any terms while studying it, or feel more confident?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Confident a bit. But mix up terms like glomerulus and nephron. Still need to revise. 😓"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, that’s normal — even experts mix terms at first. Try making a small chart: glomerulus is part of the nephron. Can you try that?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe. If I get time. Need to finish notes first. Thanks. 😴"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, finishing notes is important, but don’t forget to rest your mind too. Tell me, what’s one thing you’ll do to relax today?"
    }
  ],
